1
00:00:04,140 --> 00:00:05,220
I'm home.

2
00:00:06,260 --> 00:00:08,300
Hey, you're burning up.

3
00:00:08,300 --> 00:00:10,060
I can feel the heat radiating off you.

4
00:00:10,860 --> 00:00:14,740
Stay hydrated and get some nutrients.
Get some rest!

5
00:00:15,820 --> 00:00:16,900
I... I get it.

6
00:00:17,180 --> 00:00:20,580
It's no fun seeing you this weak.

7
00:00:32,300 --> 00:00:35,300
What is wrong with me?

8
00:00:35,860 --> 00:00:38,620
This is supposed to be a scenario I love.

9
00:00:38,980 --> 00:00:42,060
But reality is nothing like fiction.

10
00:00:43,180 --> 00:00:44,580
Leave it to your big brother.

11
00:00:45,020 --> 00:00:46,140
I am his brother.

12
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:50,500
Just a brother with no blood relation.

13
00:00:50,940 --> 00:00:52,500
Until graduation.

14
00:00:52,500 --> 00:00:54,620
We're just living together.

15
00:01:00,060 --> 00:01:03,860
What exactly do I want?
